"use strict";(self.webpackChunk_N_E=self.webpackChunk_N_E||[]).push([[3321],{96349:function(n){n.exports=JSON.parse('{"slug":"gnn","title":"GNN基础与应用","description":"","date":null,"tags":[],"category":"SearchRec","categoryId":"searchrec","content":"# GNN 基础与应用\\n\\n> **更新日期**: 2026-03-13\\n> **版本**: v1.0\\n> **难度**: 中级\\n> **预计阅读时间**: 50 分钟\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 目录\\n\\n1. [GNN 概述](#gnn-概述)\\n2. [图卷积网络 (GCN)](#图卷积网络-gcn)\\n3. [GraphSAGE](#graphsage)\\n4. [图注意力网络 (GAT)](#图注意力网络-gat)\\n5. [GNN 在推荐中的应用](#gnn-在推荐中的应用)\\n6. [面试要点](#面试要点)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## GNN 概述\\n\\n### 什么是 GNN\\n\\n图神经网络 (Graph Neural Network) 专门处理图结构数据。\\n\\n```\\n传统神经网络: 处理欧几里得数据 (图像、文本)\\nGNN: 处理非欧几里得数据 (社交网络、知识图谱、推荐系统)\\n\\n图结构: G = (V, E)\\n- V: 节点集合 (用户、商品)\\n- E: 边集合 (交互关系)\\n```\\n\\n### 推荐系统中的图\\n\\n| 图类型 | 节点 | 边 | 应用场景 |\\n|--------|------|-----|----------|\\n| 用户-商品二分图 | 用户、商品 | 交互 | 协同过滤 |\\n| 社交网络 | 用户 | 好友关系 | 社交推荐 |\\n| 知识图谱 | 实体 | 关系 | 知识增强推荐 |\\n| 序列图 | 物品 | 时序关系 | 序列推荐 |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 图卷积网络 (GCN)\\n\\n### 核心思想\\n\\nGCN 将卷积操作推广到图结构数据。\\n\\n```\\n图卷积公式:\\nH^(l+1) = σ(D^(-1/2) A D^(-1/2) H^(l) W^(l))\\n\\n其中:\\n- A: 邻接矩阵\\n- D: 度矩阵 (对角矩阵，D_ii = sum_j A_ij)\\n- H^(l): 第 l 层节点特征\\n- W^(l): 第 l 层可学习参数\\n- σ: 激活函数\\n```\\n\\n### GCN 实现\\n\\n```python\\nimport torch\\nimport torch.nn as nn\\nimport torch.nn.functional as F\\n\\nclass GCNLayer(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"GCN 层\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, in_features, out_features):\\n        super().__init__()\\n        self.linear = nn.Linear(in_features, out_features)\\n\\n    def forward(self, x, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        Args:\\n            x: [N, in_features] 节点特征\\n            adj: [N, N] 归一化邻接矩阵\\n\\n        Returns:\\n            [N, out_features]\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        # 聚合邻居信息\\n        x = torch.matmul(adj, x)\\n\\n        # 线性变换\\n        x = self.linear(x)\\n\\n        return x\\n\\n\\nclass GCN(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"图卷积网络\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, nfeat, nhid, nclass, dropout=0.5):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        self.gc1 = GCNLayer(nfeat, nhid)\\n        self.gc2 = GCNLayer(nhid, nclass)\\n        self.dropout = dropout\\n\\n    def forward(self, x, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        Args:\\n            x: [N, nfeat] 输入特征\\n            adj: [N, N] 归一化邻接矩阵\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        # 第一层\\n        x = self.gc1(x, adj)\\n        x = F.relu(x)\\n        x = F.dropout(x, self.dropout, training=self.training)\\n\\n        # 第二层\\n        x = self.gc2(x, adj)\\n\\n        return x\\n\\n\\ndef normalize_adj(adj):\\n    \\"\\"\\"\\n    对称归一化邻接矩阵: D^(-1/2) A D^(-1/2)\\n\\n    Args:\\n        adj: [N, N] 邻接矩阵\\n    \\"\\"\\"\\n    # 添加自环\\n    adj = adj + torch.eye(adj.size(0))\\n\\n    # 计算度矩阵\\n    degree = adj.sum(dim=1)\\n    degree_inv_sqrt = torch.pow(degree, -0.5)\\n    degree_inv_sqrt[torch.isinf(degree_inv_sqrt)] = 0.\\n\\n    # D^(-1/2)\\n    D_inv_sqrt = torch.diag(degree_inv_sqrt)\\n\\n    # D^(-1/2) A D^(-1/2)\\n    normalized_adj = D_inv_sqrt @ adj @ D_inv_sqrt\\n\\n    return normalized_adj\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## GraphSAGE\\n\\n### 核心思想\\n\\nGraphSAGE (SAmple and agGreGatE) 通过采样邻居来扩展到大图。\\n\\n```\\nGCN 的问题:\\n- 需要完整的邻接矩阵\\n- 内存消耗大\\n- 不能处理动态图\\n\\nGraphSAGE 改进:\\n- 采样固定数量的邻居\\n- 支持归纳学习 (inductive)\\n- 可扩展到大图\\n```\\n\\n### GraphSAGE 实现\\n\\n```python\\nclass GraphSAGELayer(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"GraphSAGE 层\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, in_features, out_features, aggregator=\'mean\'):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        self.aggregator = aggregator\\n\\n        # 自身特征和邻居特征拼接后的线性变换\\n        self.linear = nn.Linear(in_features * 2, out_features)\\n\\n    def forward(self, x, adj, sample_size=10):\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        Args:\\n            x: [N, in_features] 节点特征\\n            adj: [N, N] 邻接矩阵或邻居列表\\n            sample_size: 每个节点采样的邻居数\\n\\n        Returns:\\n            [N, out_features]\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        N = x.size(0)\\n\\n        # 采样并聚合邻居\\n        neighbor_features = []\\n\\n        for i in range(N):\\n            # 获取邻居\\n            neighbors = adj[i].nonzero(as_tuple=True)[0]\\n\\n            # 采样邻居\\n            if len(neighbors) > sample_size:\\n                sampled = neighbors[torch.randperm(len(neighbors))[:sample_size]]\\n            else:\\n                sampled = neighbors\\n\\n            # 聚合\\n            if len(sampled) > 0:\\n                neighbor_feat = x[sampled]\\n\\n                if self.aggregator == \'mean\':\\n                    aggregated = neighbor_feat.mean(dim=0)\\n                elif self.aggregator == \'max\':\\n                    aggregated = neighbor_feat.max(dim=0)[0]\\n                elif self.aggregator == \'sum\':\\n                    aggregated = neighbor_feat.sum(dim=0)\\n                else:\\n                    aggregated = neighbor_feat.mean(dim=0)\\n            else:\\n                aggregated = torch.zeros_like(x[i])\\n\\n            neighbor_features.append(aggregated)\\n\\n        neighbor_features = torch.stack(neighbor_features)\\n\\n        # 拼接自身和邻居特征\\n        combined = torch.cat([x, neighbor_features], dim=1)\\n\\n        # 线性变换\\n        output = self.linear(combined)\\n        output = F.relu(output)\\n\\n        return output\\n\\n\\nclass GraphSAGE(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"GraphSAGE 模型\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, in_features, hidden_dims, num_classes,\\n                 aggregator=\'mean\', dropout=0.5):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        self.layers = nn.ModuleList()\\n\\n        # 构建多层\\n        dims = [in_features] + hidden_dims\\n        for i in range(len(hidden_dims)):\\n            self.layers.append(\\n                GraphSAGELayer(dims[i], dims[i+1], aggregator)\\n            )\\n\\n        self.dropout = dropout\\n        self.classifier = nn.Linear(hidden_dims[-1], num_classes)\\n\\n    def forward(self, x, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"前向传播\\"\\"\\"\\n        for layer in self.layers:\\n            x = layer(x, adj)\\n            x = F.dropout(x, self.dropout, training=self.training)\\n\\n        # 节点分类\\n        logits = self.classifier(x)\\n\\n        return logits\\n\\n    def get_embeddings(self, x, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"获取节点嵌入 (用于推荐)\\"\\"\\"\\n        for layer in self.layers:\\n            x = layer(x, adj)\\n            x = F.dropout(x, self.dropout, training=self.training)\\n\\n        return x  # 节点嵌入\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 图注意力网络 (GAT)\\n\\n### 核心思想\\n\\nGAT 使用注意力机制为不同邻居分配不同权重。\\n\\n```\\nGCN: 所有邻居同等重要\\nGAT: 学习邻居的重要性权重\\n\\n注意力系数:\\ne_ij = a(W h_i, W h_j)\\nα_ij = softmax_j(e_ij)\\n\\n更新规则:\\nh_i\' = σ(sum_j α_ij W h_j)\\n```\\n\\n### GAT 实现\\n\\n```python\\nclass GATLayer(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"图注意力层\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, in_features, out_features, num_heads=8,\\n                 dropout=0.6, alpha=0.2, concat=True):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        self.in_features = in_features\\n        self.out_features = out_features\\n        self.num_heads = num_heads\\n        self.concat = concat\\n        self.dropout = dropout\\n\\n        # 多头注意力的权重矩阵\\n        self.W = nn.Parameter(torch.zeros(\\n            num_heads, in_features, out_features // num_heads\\n        ))\\n\\n        # 注意力系数参数\\n        self.a = nn.Parameter(torch.zeros(num_heads, 2 * (out_features // num_heads), 1))\\n\\n        self.leakyrelu = nn.LeakyReLU(alpha)\\n\\n        self.reset_parameters()\\n\\n    def reset_parameters(self):\\n        nn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.W)\\n        nn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.a)\\n\\n    def forward(self, x, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        Args:\\n            x: [N, in_features]\\n            adj: [N, N] 邻接矩阵\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        N = x.size(0)\\n\\n        # 线性变换: [num_heads, N, out_features//num_heads]\\n        h = torch.einsum(\'nd,hdo->hno\', x, self.W)\\n\\n        # 计算注意力系数\\n        # [h, N, 1, F\'] 和 [h, 1, N, F\'] 拼接 -> [h, N, N, 2F\']\\n        h_i = h.unsqueeze(2).expand(-1, -1, N, -1)\\n        h_j = h.unsqueeze(1).expand(-1, N, -1, -1)\\n\\n        concat = torch.cat([h_i, h_j], dim=-1)\\n\\n        # e_ij = LeakyReLU(a^T [Wh_i || Wh_j])\\n        e = self.leakyrelu(torch.einsum(\'hnmf,hfo->hnmo\', concat, self.a).squeeze(-1))\\n\\n        # Mask (只考虑邻居)\\n        mask = adj.unsqueeze(0).expand(self.num_heads, -1, -1)\\n        e = e.masked_fill(mask == 0, float(\'-inf\'))\\n\\n        # Softmax 归一化\\n        alpha = F.softmax(e, dim=-1)\\n        alpha = F.dropout(alpha, self.dropout, training=self.training)\\n\\n        # 加权聚合\\n        h_prime = torch.einsum(\'hnn,hnd->hnd\', alpha, h)\\n\\n        if self.concat:\\n            # 拼接多头: [N, num_heads * (out_features//num_heads)]\\n            return h_prime.reshape(N, -1)\\n        else:\\n            # 平均多头: [N, out_features//num_heads]\\n            return h_prime.mean(dim=0)\\n\\n\\nclass GAT(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"图注意力网络\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, nfeat, nhid, nclass, num_heads=8, dropout=0.6):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        self.gat1 = GATLayer(nfeat, nhid, num_heads=num_heads,\\n                             dropout=dropout, concat=True)\\n        self.gat2 = GATLayer(nhid * num_heads, nclass, num_heads=1,\\n                             dropout=dropout, concat=False)\\n\\n    def forward(self, x, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"前向传播\\"\\"\\"\\n        x = self.gat1(x, adj)\\n        x = F.elu(x)\\n        x = self.gat2(x, adj)\\n\\n        return x\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## GNN 在推荐中的应用\\n\\n### NGCF (Neural Graph Collaborative Filtering)\\n\\n```python\\nclass NGCFLayer(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"NGCF 层 - 神经图协同过滤\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, in_features, out_features):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        # 不同传播路径的权重\\n        self.W1 = nn.Linear(in_features, out_features)\\n        self.W2 = nn.Linear(in_features, out_features)\\n\\n    def forward(self, x, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        传播规则:\\n        e_u^(l+1) = LeakyReLU(m + e_u^l W1 + m ⊙ e_u^l W2)\\n        其中 m = sum_{i in N_u} (e_i^l / sqrt(|N_u||N_i|))\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        # 归一化邻接矩阵\\n        rowsum = adj.sum(dim=1)\\n        d_inv_sqrt = torch.pow(rowsum, -0.5)\\n        d_inv_sqrt[torch.isinf(d_inv_sqrt)] = 0.\\n        norm_adj = d_inv_sqrt.unsqueeze(1) * adj * d_inv_sqrt.unsqueeze(0)\\n\\n        # 邻居聚合\\n        neighbor_agg = torch.matmul(norm_adj, x)\\n\\n        # 消息传递\\n        m1 = self.W1(neighbor_agg)\\n        m2 = self.W2(neighbor_agg * x)\\n\\n        # 更新\\n        output = m1 + m2 + x  # 残差连接\\n        output = F.leaky_relu(output)\\n\\n        return output\\n\\n\\nclass NGCF(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"NGCF 模型\\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, n_users, n_items, embed_dim, n_layers=3, dropout=0.0):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        self.n_users = n_users\\n        self.n_items = n_items\\n        self.embed_dim = embed_dim\\n        self.n_layers = n_layers\\n\\n        # 初始化嵌入\\n        self.user_embedding = nn.Embedding(n_users, embed_dim)\\n        self.item_embedding = nn.Embedding(n_items, embed_dim)\\n\\n        # NGCF 层\\n        self.gnn_layers = nn.ModuleList([\\n            NGCFLayer(embed_dim, embed_dim) for _ in range(n_layers)\\n        ])\\n\\n        self.dropout = dropout\\n\\n        self.reset_parameters()\\n\\n    def reset_parameters(self):\\n        nn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.user_embedding.weight)\\n        nn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.item_embedding.weight)\\n\\n    def forward(self, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        Args:\\n            adj: [(n_users+n_items), (n_users+n_items)] 用户-物品二分图\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        # 初始嵌入\\n        user_emb = self.user_embedding.weight\\n        item_emb = self.item_embedding.weight\\n\\n        # 拼接用户和物品嵌入\\n        all_emb = torch.cat([user_emb, item_emb], dim=0)\\n\\n        # 存储每层的嵌入\\n        embs = [all_emb]\\n\\n        # 多层传播\\n        for layer in self.gnn_layers:\\n            all_emb = layer(all_emb, adj)\\n            all_emb = F.dropout(all_emb, self.dropout, training=self.training)\\n            embs.append(all_emb)\\n\\n        # 拼接所有层的嵌入\\n        final_emb = torch.cat(embs, dim=1)  # [N, (n_layers+1) * embed_dim]\\n\\n        # 分离用户和物品嵌入\\n        user_final_emb = final_emb[:self.n_users]\\n        item_final_emb = final_emb[self.n_users:]\\n\\n        return user_final_emb, item_final_emb\\n\\n    def get_ratings(self, user_ids):\\n        \\"\\"\\"预测评分\\"\\"\\"\\n        user_emb = self.user_embedding(user_ids)\\n        item_emb = self.item_embedding.weight\\n\\n        ratings = torch.matmul(user_emb, item_emb.t())\\n\\n        return ratings\\n```\\n\\n### LightGCN\\n\\n```python\\nclass LightGCN(nn.Module):\\n    \\"\\"\\"\\n    LightGCN - 轻量级图卷积网络\\n\\n    特点:\\n    - 去除特征变换和非线性激活\\n    - 只保留邻居聚合\\n    - 更高效，性能更好\\n    \\"\\"\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, n_users, n_items, embed_dim, n_layers=3):\\n        super().__init__()\\n\\n        self.n_users = n_users\\n        self.n_items = n_items\\n        self.embed_dim = embed_dim\\n        self.n_layers = n_layers\\n\\n        # 初始化嵌入\\n        self.user_embedding = nn.Embedding(n_users, embed_dim)\\n        self.item_embedding = nn.Embedding(n_items, embed_dim)\\n\\n        self.reset_parameters()\\n\\n    def reset_parameters(self):\\n        nn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.user_embedding.weight)\\n        nn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.item_embedding.weight)\\n\\n    def forward(self, adj):\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        传播规则:\\n        e^(k+1) = D^(-1/2) A D^(-1/2) e^k\\n\\n        简化: 没有 W 和激活函数\\n        \\"\\"\\"\\n        # 初始嵌入\\n        all_emb = torch.cat([\\n            self.user_embedding.weight,\\n            self.item_embedding.weight\\n        ], dim=0)\\n\\n        embs = [all_emb]\\n\\n        # 归一化邻接矩阵\\n        rowsum = adj.sum(dim=1)\\n        d_inv_sqrt = torch.pow(rowsum, -0.5)\\n        d_inv_sqrt[torch.isinf(d_inv_sqrt)] = 0.\\n        norm_adj = d_inv_sqrt.unsqueeze(1) * adj * d_inv_sqrt.unsqueeze(0)\\n\\n        # 多层传播 (只有聚合)\\n        for _ in range(self.n_layers):\\n            all_emb = torch.matmul(norm_adj, all_emb)\\n            embs.append(all_emb)\\n\\n        # 平均所有层的嵌入\\n        final_emb = sum(embs) / len(embs)\\n\\n        user_emb = final_emb[:self.n_users]\\n        item_emb = final_emb[self.n_users:]\\n\\n        return user_emb, item_emb\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 面试要点\\n\\n### 高频问题\\n\\n**Q1: GNN 相比传统方法的优点？**\\n\\nA:\\n1. 显式建模关系结构\\n2. 端到端学习\\n3. 可融合多源信息\\n4. 可扩展性强\\n\\n**Q2: GCN 和 GraphSAGE 的区别？**\\n\\nA:\\n| 维度 | GCN | GraphSAGE |\\n|------|-----|-----------|\\n| 聚合 | 全图 | 采样邻居 |\\n| 训练方式 | 直推式 | 归纳式 |\\n| 扩展性 | 差 | 好 |\\n\\n**Q3: GAT 的注意力机制是什么？**\\n\\nA:\\n- 为每个邻居学习一个权重\\n- 通过可学习的注意力参数计算\\n- 权重表示邻居的重要性\\n\\n**Q4: NGCF 和 LightGCN 的区别？**\\n\\nA:\\n- NGCF: 包含特征变换、非线性激活\\n- LightGCN: 只保留邻居聚合，更轻量、效果更好\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 相关文档\\n\\n- [协同过滤算法](/kb/searchrec/) - 传统 CF\\n- [DIN与DIEN](/kb/searchrec/dindien) - 深度推荐\\n- [DeepFM家族](/kb/searchrec/deepfm) - 特征交叉\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 参考文献\\n\\n1. Kipf & Welling. \\"Semi-Supervised Classification with Graph Convolutional Networks\\". 2017.\\n2. Hamilton et al. \\"Inductive Representation Learning on Large Graphs\\". 2017.\\n3. Veličković et al. \\"Graph Attention Networks\\". 2018.\\n4. Wang et al. \\"Neural Graph Collaborative Filtering\\". 2019.\\n5. He et al. \\"LightGCN: Simplifying and Powering Graph Convolution Network\\". 2020.\\n","filePath":"图神经网络/GNN基础与应用.md"}')}}]);